<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 0;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 200px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .gallery {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .gallery img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #9c8b7a;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .social-links a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #9c8b7a;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <img src="{{ company_logo }}" alt="Design Gaga" class="logo">
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        {% if variant == 'modern_minimal' %}
        <h1>Welcome to Design Gaga's Curated Spaces</h1>
        <p>Dear {{ lead.name }},</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for your interest in elevating your property's presence. At Design Gaga, we specialize in creating minimalist, modern spaces that speak volumes through thoughtful design and careful curation.</p>
        
        <div class="gallery">
            {% for image in modern_portfolio[:4] %}
            <img src="{{ image.url }}" alt="{{ image.description }}">
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        
        <p>Our approach combines contemporary aesthetics with functional luxury, ensuring your property not only looks exceptional but feels inherently welcoming.</p>
        
        {% else %}
        <h1>Welcome to Design Gaga's Luxury Staging Collection</h1>
        <p>Dear {{ lead.name }},</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for considering Design Gaga for your property staging needs. We specialize in creating timeless, elegant spaces that capture the essence of luxury living while maintaining a warm, inviting atmosphere.</p>
        
        <div class="gallery">
            {% for image in classic_portfolio[:4] %}
            <img src="{{ image.url }}" alt="{{ image.description }}">
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
        
        <p>Our classic approach to luxury staging combines traditional elegance with contemporary comfort, ensuring your property stands out in the luxury market.</p>
        {% endif %}
        
        <p>Would you be interested in discussing how we can transform your space? I'd love to schedule a personal consultation to explore ideas tailored to your property.</p>
        
        <a href="{{ booking_link }}" class="cta-button">Schedule a Consultation</a>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        {{ agent.name }}<br>
        Lead Designer, Design Gaga</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="{{ social.instagram }}">Instagram</a>
            <a href="{{ social.linkedin }}">LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="{{ social.facebook }}">Facebook</a>
        </div>
        <p>Design Gaga | Luxury Home Staging<br>
        {{ company.address }}<br>
        {{ company.phone }}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
